{"tid":1647013,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「連仔救香港」支持重登帳號同改密碼嘅入嚟啊","createTime":"2019-10-11T14:31:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T16:22:15.000Z","uid":133763,"like":80,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"f649cf411798d819ff2022a7d27ee4e1ea243306","tid":1647013,"uid":133763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T14:31:11.000Z","msg":"本人絕對相信<br />\n<br />\n二千多名手足有受到恐嚇<br />\n<br />\n被要求交出手機所有資料<br />\n<br />\n包括連登帳號<br />\n<br />\n鑒於連登出現大量奇怪，亂帶風向主題<br />\n<br />\n靠P牌及起底判斷會員身份並不足夠<br />\n<br />\n所以<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">我們</span></span></span></strong>懇請連仔<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">強制登出所有會員帳號<br />\n並強制要求會員更改密碼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我知站務台有好多呢啲post<br />\n不過冇人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">宜家一人一post推撚爆佢啦<br />\n<br />\n仲想贏就幫手啦</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">邊個反對我就係鬼</span><br />\n<br />\n連仔肯做 絕對係英雄之中嘅英雄<br />\n<br />\n無論你技術上做唔做到<br />\n<br />\n你都可以話比大家知<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">最後 ios13好撚多簡體字</span>"},{"pid":"9380b56469c72d238ecb73affab06776c86e13f4","tid":1647013,"uid":135798,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T14:33:47.000Z","msg":"每12點就強制登出所有會員帳號有無得諗？"},{"pid":"166cd7c3a7f8d70d0ad3827c53201f59f94c1066","tid":1647013,"uid":259329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T14:34:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a33c9aef1ab9ec9d662764e78cfb1fea5d64aa36","tid":1647013,"uid":284708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T14:34:58.000Z","msg":"P牌用念力幫你推同埋表示支持"},{"pid":"931495302a45f791fffc04056f06a7e5ff7bd7ce","tid":1647013,"uid":133763,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9380b56469c72d238ec